---
layout: base.njk
title: Beta Collection
description: "Tracking my progress toward a complete Limited Edition Beta set of Magic: the Gathering."
permalink: /beta/
---

<article>
    <h1>Beta Collection</h1>

    <p>
        I'm working toward a complete <em>Limited Edition Beta</em> set of <em>Magic: the Gathering</em>,
        and I'd rather trade my way there than buy my way there. If you see something on my want list
        that you can help with, <a href="/contact/">get in touch</a>.
    </p>

    <div class="beta-progress">
        <div class="beta-progress-stats">
            <span class="beta-stat">{{ beta.owned }}&thinsp;/&thinsp;{{ beta.total }} cards</span>
            <span class="beta-stat">{{ beta.percent }}% complete</span>
        </div>
        <div class="beta-progress-bar">
            <div class="beta-progress-fill" style="width: {{ beta.percent }}%"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="beta-color-bars">
        {% for color in beta.colorOrder %}
        {% set stats = beta.colorStats[color] %}
        <div class="beta-color-row">
            <span class="beta-color-label">{{ beta.colorLabels[color] }}</span>
            <div class="beta-progress-bar beta-progress-bar-sm">
                <div class="beta-progress-fill" style="width: {{ stats.percent }}%"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="beta-color-count">{{ stats.owned }}/{{ stats.total }}</span>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>

    {% if beta.unrecognized.length > 0 %}
    <div class="beta-warning">
        <strong>Warning:</strong> unrecognized card names in your data file:
        {{ beta.unrecognized | join(", ") }}.
        Check for typos in <code>src/_data/beta.js</code>.
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <h2>Want List</h2>

    <p class="text-muted text-small">{{ beta.needed }} cards remaining. Last updated {{ beta.lastUpdated }}.</p>

    {% for r in ["R", "U", "C"] %}
    {% set rCards = beta.neededByRarity[r] %}
    {% if rCards.length > 0 %}
    <h3>{{ beta.rarityLabels[r] }} <span class="text-muted text-small">({{ rCards.length }})</span></h3>
    <ul class="beta-cards">
        {% for card in rCards %}
        <li>{{ card.name }}<span class="beta-type">{{ card.type }}</span></li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}

    {% if beta.tradeable.length > 0 %}
    <h2>For Trade</h2>
    <p class="text-muted text-small">Beta cards I have extras of.</p>
    <ul class="beta-cards">
        {% for card in beta.tradeable %}
        <li>{{ card.name }}{% if card.note %}<span class="beta-note">{{ card.note }}</span>{% endif %}</li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% endif %}

    <h2>Full Set</h2>

    {% for color in beta.colorOrder %}
    {% set colorCards = beta.byColor[color] %}
    {% set stats = beta.colorStats[color] %}
    <details{% if stats.needed > 0 %} open{% endif %}>
        <summary>{{ beta.colorLabels[color] }} &mdash; {{ stats.owned }}/{{ stats.total }}</summary>
        <ul class="beta-cards">
            {% for card in colorCards %}
            <li class="{% if card.have %}have{% else %}need{% endif %}">
                <span class="beta-card-name">{{ card.name }}</span>
                <span class="beta-rarity">{{ card.rarity }}</span>
                {% if card.note %}<span class="beta-note">{{ card.note }}</span>{% endif %}
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
    </details>
    {% endfor %}

</article>
